---
title: Vegan Spicy Buffalo Chickpea Sandwiches with Blue Corn Tortilla Chips & Green Salad
description: This week, the humble chickpea is transformed into a bold and hearty vegan dinner idea sure to evoke the zestiest of game days—in just 10 minutes! Mashed chickpeas are combined with vegan mayo, zippy scallions, and Frank’s Seasoning and Hot Sauce for a hot-and-spicy filling with a perfectly creamy texture (hello, Buffalo!). It’s loaded onto crisp toasted sourdough and topped with a heap of crisp dressed greens. Crunchy blue corn chips and any extra salad come along for this dinner ride.
